Weekly Cleansing Day
This swimming pool will be closed for weekly cleansing operation from 10:00am to 6:00pm on every Wednesday. The pool will resume open at 7:00pm of the same day. (If the weekly cleansing day falls on a public holiday, the swimming pool will open as usual. The weekly cleansing operation will be rescheduled on Friday of the same week.)
